---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteShell from '../components/SiteShell.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---


<Layout
  title="About Us | COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT)"
  description="COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT) is a leading Congolese company providing complete industrial solutions, equipment, and services."
>
  <SiteShell activePath="/about">
    <main>
      <!-- Page Hero -->
      <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="hero-bg">
          <img src={site.gallery[5].src} alt={site.gallery[5].alt} />
          <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-content section">
          <p class="hero-eyebrow">Company Profile</p>
          <h1>Expertise at the Service of Your Success</h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">
            COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT) is a leading Congolese company, recognized for its expertise in providing complete industrial solutions. Since its inception, CGT has been committed to delivering high-quality services, ranging from the design and supply of industrial equipment to its installation and maintenance. We specialize in several fields including the supply of various industrial products, electrical, mechanical, instrumentation, electrowinning, screen panels, drilling safety gaskets, motors, gear boxes, mechanical seals, equipment spares, pumps, valves, pressure and temperature transmitters, industrial filters, high quality reagents, chemicals, laboratory equipment, personal protective equipment (PPE), conveyor belt accessories. With a team of seasoned experts, we offer customized solutions tailored to our clients' specific needs, ensuring their complete satisfaction.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Commitments -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <div class="section">
          <h2>Our Commitments</h2>
          <p>
            Since its founding in 2023, COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT) has been dedicated to offering tailored solutions and exceptional service to its clients. Driven by an experienced team passionate about innovation, the company places adaptability, excellence, and a commitment to quality at the heart of its activities. These core values guide every action we take and form the foundation of our success, enabling CGT to build strong relationships with partners and maintain its reputation as a recognized expert in the industrial solutions sector.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Vision and Mission -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <div class="section">
          <h2>Vision and Mission</h2>
          <h3>Vision</h3>
          <p>
            COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT) aims to become the undisputed leader in providing industrial solutions in the Democratic Republic of Congo. We strive to be the preferred partner for businesses, offering products and services of impeccable quality that meet the specific needs of each sector.
          </p>
          <h3>Mission</h3>
          <p>
            Our mission is to provide comprehensive and innovative solutions tailored to our clients' specific requirements. We are committed to delivering exceptional after-sales service and maintaining long-lasting relationships based on trust. By combining technical expertise with a personalized approach, we exceed our clients' expectations at every stage of their projects.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Our Values -->
      <section class="values-section">
        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <p class="eyebrow">Our Values</p>
            <h2>The core values of COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT) are the foundation of our success and guide every aspect of our business. These values are:</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="values-grid">
            <article class="value-card">
              <h3>Excellence</h3>
              <p>We are committed to providing the highest quality products and services, in compliance with the strictest standards and our clients' expectations.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="value-card">
              <h3>Innovation</h3>
              <p>We are constantly seeking innovative solutions to meet industrial challenges and anticipate the evolving needs of our clients.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="value-card">
              <h3>Adaptability</h3>
              <p>We are flexible in responding to market demands and the unique requirements of each project, offering tailored solutions.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="value-card">
              <h3>Commitment</h3>
              <p>We build long-term, trusting relationships with our clients, being a reliable and responsive partner.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Products and Services -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <div class="section">
          <h2>Our Products and Services</h2>
          <p>At COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT), we not only provide high-quality products but also offer comprehensive solutions and personalized support to meet the specific needs of our clients. Below is a detailed overview of our main products and services:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Laboratory:</strong> Industrial, Medical</li>
            <li><strong>Industrial Filtration</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Pumps:</strong> Multistage pumps, Chemical pumps, Clear water pumps, Dosing pumps</li>
            <li><strong>Valves:</strong> Diaphragm valves, Guillotine valves, Pinch valves, Butterfly valves</li>
            <li><strong>Electrical:</strong> Cable trunking boxes, Electrical plugs and sockets, Electric motors, Electrical panels and switchgear, Circuit breakers, Mini substations, Transformers, Generators, Solar lighting, Cables, Cable ends and sleeves</li>
            <li><strong>Instrumentation:</strong> Transmitters, Flow meters, Vibration monitoring sensors, Probes</li>
            <li><strong>Conveyor Belts:</strong> Conveyor belt accessories, Pulleys, Floor plates, V-plough scrapers, Impact, return, and curve idlers, Tension and primary pulleys, Wear plates, Couplings, Reducers, Rollers, Drums (conductive and non-conductive)</li>
            <li><strong>Geomembrane:</strong> Supply, installation, and repair of geomembranes for various industrial applications.</li>
            <li><strong>Personal Protective Equipment (PPE):</strong> Safety helmets, Rubber boots, Safety shoes, Work clothing (white lab coats and acid-resistant), Earplugs (reusable and with cords), Leather gloves, Helmet protection nets, PVC gloves, Work lamps and belts, Rain suits and reflectors, Protective glasses (dark and clear), Dust masks</li>
            <li><strong>Plates, Pipes and Electrowinning:</strong> Metal plates in various sizes, Stainless steel 316L plates and pipes, Cathodes, Anodes, Demister Balls, Edge strips</li>
            <li><strong>Mechanical Welding and HDPE Pipe Welding:</strong> Specialized welding services for the maintenance and installation of industrial equipment.</li>
            <li><strong>Crusher:</strong> Supply of products and maintenance services for industrial crushers.</li>
            <li><strong>Other Products:</strong> Paints, Screws and nuts, Bulk bags, Chocking blocks, Straps, Cement, Padlocks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Teams and Partners -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <div class="section">
          <h2>Our Teams and Partners</h2>
          <p>At COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT), we firmly believe that the success of our company relies on the expertise and dedication of our team. Composed of highly qualified and experienced professionals, our team is constantly trained to offer tailored and innovative solutions to each client. We work closely with a trusted network of partners across various industrial sectors, enabling us to ensure exceptional quality and reliability for every project.</p>
          <p>We value strong and lasting relationships with our partners, and we always strive to exceed our clients' expectations by fostering effective and harmonious collaborations.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Our Partners -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <div class="section">
          <h2>Our Partners</h2>
          <p>COPAK GENERAL TRADING (CGT) has built strong strategic partnerships with renowned companies and suppliers, both nationally and internationally. These collaborations allow us to offer high-quality solutions while gaining access to the latest innovations and technologies. We are committed to working with partners who share our values of excellence, innovation, and reliability, enabling us to expand our offerings and guarantee optimal solutions for our clients in a timely and efficient manner.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Info -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <div class="section">
          <h2>Contact Information</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +243 89 798 0803 | +27 677584446</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> info@copakgt.com</li>
            <li><strong>Website:</strong> https://www.copakgt.com</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> Av: 33 Tony Mwana Q/ Golf Karavia plateaux 3 C/ Annexe, Lubumbashi, Haut Katanga, RDC.</li>
            <li><strong>RCCM:</strong> CD/LSH/RCCM/24-B-00695</li>
            <li><strong>ID NAT:</strong> 05-S9502-N58278L</li>
            <li><strong>NUMERO IMPOT:</strong> A2408513F</li>
            <li><strong>ARSP:</strong> 6209253671</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </SiteShell>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-hero {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 50vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-bg {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
	}

	.hero-bg img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.hero-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(26, 58, 42, 0.9) 0%, rgba(26, 58, 42, 0.5) 100%);
	}

	.hero-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		padding: 5rem 0;
		max-width: 640px;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.hero-eyebrow {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.hero-content h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.hero-sub {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
		margin: 0;
	}

	.content-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.two-col {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.col-text h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.col-text p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.75;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.col-image {
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
	}

	.col-image img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: 380px;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.values-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--surface);
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.value-card {
		padding: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		transition: all 0.25s ease;
	}

	.value-card:hover {
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.value-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.value-card p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.65;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.process-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.process-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.process-card {
		padding: 2rem;
		background: var(--surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
	}

	.process-num {
		display: inline-block;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--primary-light);
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.process-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
	}

	.process-card p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.65;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.team-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--surface);
	}

	.team-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.team-card {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
	}

	.team-avatar {
		width: 4rem;
		height: 4rem;
		margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--primary);
		color: #fff;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.team-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.team-role {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--primary-light);
		font-weight: 500;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.team-card p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.65;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.photos-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.photos-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.photo-card {
		margin: 0;
		position: relative;
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.photo-card img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: 260px;
		object-fit: cover;
		transition: transform 0.4s ease;
	}

	.photo-card:hover img {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}

	.photo-card figcaption {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem;
		background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7));
		color: #fff;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
	}

	.photo-card:hover figcaption {
		opacity: 1;
	}

	.photo-card figcaption strong {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.photo-card figcaption span {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
	}

	@media (max-width: 960px) {
		.two-col,
		.values-grid,
		.process-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		}

		.team-grid,
		.photos-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.two-col,
		.values-grid,
		.process-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.page-hero {
			min-height: 40vh;
		}
	}
</style>